data.description: Welcome Home!  This charming, 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is in Anderson Creek Club - a highly desired, gated, golf-course community.  The first floor features open-concept living between the kitchen and living rooms, formal dining, and breakfast nook.  There is a flex room with vaulted ceiling perfect for a home office or play room.  The primary bedroom, and 2 additional bedrooms, are also located on the first floor! Upstairs is the fourth bedroom.  The outdoor space is built for entertaining with a screened porch, custom fire pit, and privacy. Sellers are offering a $1,000 carpet allowance!  *Anderson Creek POA dues include 100 mgbs fiber optic internet, pool, lap pool, fitness center, splash pad & much more*
